data.description: Excellent location for this Longwood historic area 6 Bedroom 4 Bathrooms ready to move into house! Enjoy your new Kitchen granite countertop looking into the open floor plan living room. Relax in your Great Room or large Master Bedroom with 4 more bedrooms upstairs. Another downstairs bedroom or office give plenty of space to spread out. Lots of fun with your screened pool or play in the fenced in backyard. Enjoy the calm of nature with no back neighbors. Walk to restaurants or Reiter Park with farmers markets and festivals. The Longwood Sunrail station is close for a no drive trip to Orlando and beyond. Large flex room upstairs can function as a second family room/game room or converted into another bedroom. Click on the virtual tour for a 3D Matterport where you can "walk through" the house as if you were there.
